{"tid":55322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實而家啲警察係咪廢","createTime":"2016-12-26T10:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T10:03:52.000Z","uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3822b6480caa61ca5eca902d7a67e7ec0d303b20","tid":55322,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"唔係講能力方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭先我見對面有三個警察 一個白衫兩個藍衫<br />\n咁我就望一望個白衫咩樣啦 睇下咩年紀做到白衫咁巴閉  <br />\n結果我一望佢即刻dup低個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得隻死狗噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然都可能係我毒親佢哋 不忍直視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心諗而家啲警察係咪咁廢 冇啲自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  都冇嗰種阻嚇性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話   諗起我老豆以前話  見過差佬遇到賊搶劫定唔知咩，有槍嘅 結果兩個差佬同我老豆一齊匿埋等支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最記得我老豆仲同我講話差佬都係打份工 ,唔會搵命搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}